Package: tracks
Title: Easily build genomic tracks
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("Charles", "Joly Beauparlant",
    email = "Charles.Joly-Beauparlant@crchul.ulaval.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This packages uses GenomicRanges, GenomicAlignments and ggbio to
    create tracks of a selected regions. It takes as input a list of bam files,
    a genomic region in GRanges format and (optionnaly) an annotation.
Depends: R (>= 3.2.2)
License: Artistic-2.0
LazyData: true
Imports:
    ggbio,
    GenomicAlignments,
    metagene
